    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-UKUI SIG 是什么？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler sig-UKUI SIG（Special Interest Group，特别兴趣小组）负责 The UKUI team is responsible for the development and maintenance of UKUI desktop in openeuler community.。该 SIG 共有 9 名核心成员，维护 148 个代码仓库，属于 桌面与图形界面 领域。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "如何参与 openEuler sig-UKUI SIG？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "参与 openEuler sig-UKUI SIG 的方式：1）向相关仓库（如 openeuler/ukui、openeuler/kylin-user-guide、openeuler/kylin-installer）提交 Pull Request；2）订阅邮件列表 ukui@openeuler.org；3）参加 SIG 定期工作会议，会议信息见 openEuler 官网活动日历。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-UKUI SIG 包含哪些代码仓库？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler sig-UKUI SIG 共维护 148 个代码仓库，主要包括：openeuler/ukui、openeuler/kylin-user-guide、openeuler/kylin-installer 等。完整列表见 https://www.openeuler.org/zh/sig/sig-UKUI。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-UKUI SIG 的 Maintainer 是谁？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler sig-UKUI SIG 现有 6 名 Maintainer，包括：Li Jianfeng、Dou Yan、Hua Yadong。Maintainer 负责代码最终审核与合并。"
        }
      }
    ]
